Standards-Version: 4.5.0
Homepage: https://build2.org/

Package: build2
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: C++ Build Tool (b) from build2 toolchain
 build2 is an open source (Expat), cross-platform build tool from
 build2-toolchain for developing and packaging C++ code.
 This package contains build tool (b). Other tools
 (bdep, bpkg) are in build2-tools package.

Package: libbuild2-0.13
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: shared library for build2 tool
 This package provides shared library for build2 tool.
 .
 build2 is an open source (Expat), cross-platform build tool from
 build2-toolchain for developing and packaging C++ code.
 .
 build2-toolchain is a hierarchy of tools that includes the build
 system (b), package dependency manager (bpkg) for 
 package consumption, and project dependency manager (bdep)
 for project development.
 build2-toolchain provides similar functionality like
 conan+cmake+make or vcpkg+cmake+make.

Package: libbutl-0.13
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: shared library for build2, bpkg, bdep tools
 Shared runtime library for build2 (b) and build2-tools (bdep, bpkg).

Package: build2-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 libc6-dev | libc-dev,
 build2 (= ${binary:Version}),
 libbuild2-0.13 (= ${binary:Version}),
 libbutl-0.13   (= ${binary:Version}),
Description: build2 development libraries and headers
 This package contains the header files and libraries for
 build2 - an open source (Expat), cross-platform build tool from
 build2-toolchain.
